## 2. Vision & Goals

### üéØ Primary Goals

| Goal | Description | Metric |
|------|-------------|--------|
| **Seamless Ordering** | Customer order tanpa perlu staff | < 3 min average |
| **Data Collection** | Capture WhatsApp + TikTok | 100% customers |
| **Lucky Draw Integration** | Auto-qualify eligible purchases | 5:1 rule enforced |
| **Viral Marketing** | Encourage TikTok posting | 50%+ post rate |
| **Queue Management** | Reduce wait confusion | Real-time estimation |

### üåü Core Principles

1. **Maintain Retro CRT Aesthetic** - The unique visual identity stays
2. **Human-like AI Interaction** - Nina talks like a real person
3. **Zero Friction** - Minimum steps, maximum conversion
4. **Viral by Design** - Every touchpoint encourages TikTok posting
5. **Mobile-First** - 90% of customers will use smartphones

---

