### 3.2 Key Decision Points

| Point | Condition | Result |
|-------|-----------|--------|
| **Qty Check** | Qty < 5 | ‚ùå No Lucky Draw ID |
| **Qty Check** | Qty = 5-9 | ‚úÖ 1 Ticket |
| **Qty Check** | Qty ‚â• 10 | ‚úÖ 2 Tickets (VVIP) |
| **TikTok Post** | Not posted | Ticket dormant |
| **TikTok Post** | Posted + verified | Ticket ACTIVATED |
| **Selfie** | Not taken | Reminder sent |
| **Selfie** | Taken + uploaded | Entry complete |

