## 8. Payment System

### 8.1 Payment Flow


text
‚îå‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îê
‚îÇ                    PAYMENT OPTIONS                              ‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î§
‚îÇ                                                                 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   OPTION A: BAYAR ONLINE                                        ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ                                         ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   1. Customer selects "Bayar Online"                            ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   2. Redirect to Stripe/PayHere checkout                        ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   3. Payment success ‚Üí Auto-generate queue number               ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   4. WhatsApp notification sent                                 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   5. Order appears on Staff Panel                               ‚îÇ
‚îÇ                                                                 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   Supported Methods:                                            ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ QR Pay (BIBD, Baiduri for Brunei)                          ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Credit/Debit Card                                           ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ E-Wallets (GrabPay, ShopeePay if available)                ‚îÇ
‚îÇ                                                                 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ    ‚îÇ
‚îÇ                                                                 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   OPTION B: BAYAR DI KAUNTER                                    ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ‚îÅ                                       ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   1. Customer selects "Bayar Di Kaunter"                        ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   2. Generate temporary ORDER CODE (not queue number)           ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   3. Customer shows code at counter                             ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   4. Staff retrieves order, accepts payment                     ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   5. Staff marks as PAID ‚Üí Queue number assigned                ‚îÇ
‚îÇ   6. WhatsApp notification sent                                 ‚îÇ
‚îÇ                                                                 ‚îÇ
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò


### 8.2 Payment Gateway Options (Brunei)

| Provider | Features | Setup Cost |
|----------|----------|------------|
| **Stripe** | Card payments, global | Free signup |
| **PayHere** | SEA-focused, QR | Varies |
| **BIBD QR** | Local Brunei bank | Business account |
| **Manual** | Cash/card at counter | Free |

**Recommendation:** Start with Manual + Stripe for MVP

---

## 9. Queue Management

### 9.1 Queue Number Format


text
[PREFIX]-[4-DIGIT-SEQ]

Prefixes:
‚Ä¢ A = Online payment orders
‚Ä¢ B = Counter payment orders
‚Ä¢ V = VVIP orders (10+ items)

Examples:
‚Ä¢ A-0047 = 47th online order
‚Ä¢ B-0012 = 12th counter order
‚Ä¢ V-0003 = 3rd VVIP order


### 9.2 Wait Time Calculation


text
ESTIMATED_WAIT = (ORDERS_AHEAD √ó AVG_PREP_TIME) / NUM_STAFF

Example:
‚Ä¢ 3 orders ahead
‚Ä¢ 3 minutes average prep
‚Ä¢ 2 staff working
‚Ä¢ Wait = (3 √ó 3) / 2 = 4.5 minutes ‚Üí Display "~5 minit"


### 9.3 Real-time Updates

| Event | Customer Notification | Staff Action |
|-------|----------------------|--------------|
| Order received | WhatsApp: "Pesanan diterima!" | Shows in queue |
| Preparing | Screen update: "Preparing..." | Mark "In Progress" |
| Ready | WhatsApp + Call: "Order siap!" | Mark "Ready" |
| Collected | - | Mark "Complete" |

---

## 10. TikTok Viral Loop

### 10.1 Verification Flow


text
CUSTOMER POSTS TIKTOK:
1. Create video with product
2. Tag @styloairpool
3. Use #AbangColek2026
4. Copy video URL

VERIFICATION PROCESS:
1. Customer submits URL in verification screen
2. System extracts video ID
3. Check for hashtag presence (manual for now, or TikTok API)
4. Staff verification option (manual confirm)
5. Entry marked as ACTIVATED

FUTURE AUTOMATION (TikTok API):
‚Ä¢ Webhook to detect new posts with hashtag
‚Ä¢ Auto-verify @styloairpool tags
‚Ä¢ Auto-activate entries


### 10.2 Instant Rewards

| Action | Reward |
|--------|--------|
| Take selfie (uploaded) | Entry to queue for free item |
| Post TikTok (verified) | Free mineral water |
| Get 1000+ views | Additional lucky draw chance |

