## 14. UI/UX Design Direction

### 14.1 Visual Identity (Maintained)

| Element | Style |
|---------|-------|
| **CRT Screen** | Scanlines, flicker, green phosphor |
| **Typography** | VT323 monospace |
| **Colors** | Green glow, amber, red accents |
| **Animations** | Retro, pixel-perfect |
| **Sound** | Beeps, arcade-style |

### 14.2 New Elements

| Element | Style |
|---------|-------|
| **Prize Cards** | Metallic gradient, pulse glow |
| **Buttons** | 3D beveled, arcade-style |
| **Forms** | CRT terminal input style |
| **Loading** | ASCII progress bars |
| **Success States** | Confetti + CRT flash |

### 14.3 Screen Transitions

| From ‚Üí To | Animation |
|-----------|-----------|
| Splash ‚Üí Promo | Fade dissolve |
| Promo ‚Üí Order | Slide left |
| Order ‚Üí Cart | Slide left |
| Cart ‚Üí Payment | Slide left |
| Any ‚Üí Confirmation | Zoom + confetti |

