Copy-paste ini:

Use the sequentialthinking tool.

Objective: Create a new greenfield app "abang-colek-kiosk-v2" inside this monorepo to implement the v2.0 proposal (10 screens, queue, lucky draw, staff panel) with a clean architecture.

Requirements:
1) Scaffold a Vite + React + TypeScript PWA app with:
