Codex prompt (create landing page with your brand energy)

Copy-paste into Codex:

Use the sequentialthinking tool.

Objective: Build a high-converting landing page for ABANG COLEK KIOSK v2.0 inside the existing React app (abang-colek-brand-os).

Requirements:
1) Route:
- Make "/" render the LandingPage.
- Add a top nav with links to /c/splash, /k/display, /s/queue, /a/dashboard.

2) Sections (conversion-focused):
- Hero: "Voice-Powered POS + Lucky Draw System" with 2 CTAs:
  Primary: "Mula Order" -> /c/splash
  Secondary: "Kiosk Mode" -> /k/display
- Social proof strip: "Queue bergerak laju ‚Ä¢ WhatsApp updates ‚Ä¢ Lucky Draw activation"
- How it works: 4-step cards (Scan QR -> Order via voice -> Pay -> Collect + Selfie/TikTok)
- Lucky Draw teaser: rules (5=1 ticket, 10=2 tickets) + upcoming draw date
- Staff/Admin block: small card area with links to staff/admin modes (auth-gated later)
- Footer: contact + disclaimer + version label

3) Design system:
- Must match ABANG COLEK brand: modern street + CRT accent (scanlines, glow) but not too heavy.
- Use reusable components (Button, Card, CRTPanel, Scanlines overlay) if available; otherwise create minimal ones.
- Fully responsive (mobile-first) and fast (no heavy images required).

