1) Product Hierarchy yang kemas

NIAGAHUB = platform / SaaS umbrella

Abang Colek = salah satu merchant/tenant (template ‚ÄúStreet-CRT / Voice POS + Lucky Draw‚Äù)

Ini penting untuk:

scaling onboarding peniaga lain

monetization (subscription/fees)

governance (roles, billing, compliance)

2) Naming & Route Strategy (platform-grade)

Saya cadangkan struktur URL begini:

/ ‚Üí NIAGAHUB Landing (platform)

/m/:slug ‚Üí Merchant Landing (contoh: /m/abang-colek)

/m/:slug/c/* ‚Üí Customer flow

/m/:slug/k/* ‚Üí Kiosk mode

/m/:slug/s/* ‚Üí Staff panel

/m/:slug/a/* ‚Üí Admin dashboard

Outcome: satu deployment, ramai peniaga, semua flow scoped ikut merchant.

3) Brand System (white-label ready)

