merchant.theme (colors, fonts, CRT on/off)

merchant.assets (logo, posters, background)

merchant.copy (tagline, WhatsApp templates)

merchant.campaign_rules (Lucky Draw 5:1, VIP tiers)

Abang Colek akan jadi preset theme: theme_preset = "street_crt".

