ABANG-COLEK adalah USER YANG 1st Menggunakan SERVICE NIAGAHUB

Faham. Kita lock-in positioning ini:

NIAGAHUB = platform / service provider (multi-merchant SaaS)

ABANG-COLEK = merchant pertama (first customer / flagship tenant)

Ini adalah setup yang ideal untuk go-to-market kerana anda boleh gunakan ABANG-COLEK sebagai reference implementation dan ‚Äúcase study tenant‚Äù untuk onboarding peniaga lain.

Berikut ialah blueprint yang anda patut enforce dalam code + database supaya model ini ‚Äúenterprise-safe‚Äù.

1) Tenant Model (Flagship Tenant Pattern)
Core entities

niagahub_platform (implicit‚Äîyour app)

merchants table (Abang Colek = row pertama)

merchant_users (staff/admin untuk merchant)

platform_admins (anda sebagai super admin)

Rule: semua data transaksi mesti scoped dengan merchant_id.

2) Routing & UX (Single App, Multi-tenant)

Kita kekalkan satu app sahaja, tetapi semua flows merchant-scoped:

Platform landing: /

Merchant landing: /m/:slug

Customer: /m/:slug/c/*

Kiosk: /m/:slug/k/*

Staff: /m/:slug/s/*

Admin: /m/:slug/a/*

Abang Colek akan accessible sebagai:

/m/abang-colek/c/splash (customer)

/m/abang-colek/k/display (kiosk)

/m/abang-colek/s/queue (staff)

/m/abang-colek/a/dashboard (admin)

3) Data Ownership & Security Boundary (Supabase-first)

Minimum schema (platform-ready):

merchants(id, slug, name, theme_preset, created_at)

merchant_locations(id, merchant_id, name, timezone)

products(id, merchant_id, name, price, active)

orders(id, merchant_id, location_id, status, total_items, total_amount, customer_phone, customer_tiktok, created_at)

order_items(id, merchant_id, order_id, product_id, qty, unit_price)

queue_status(id, merchant_id, order_id, queue_number, status, estimated_wait, updated_at)

campaigns(id, merchant_id, type, event_code, rules_json, active)

lucky_draw_entries(id, merchant_id, order_id, lucky_draw_id, tickets, status, selfie_url, tiktok_url, verified_at)

RLS principle (must-have)

Public customer routes boleh create orders hanya under the merchant slug they‚Äôre in.

Staff/Admin hanya boleh access data merchant mereka.

Platform admin boleh access all merchants.

