6) ‚ÄúGovernance‚Äù decisions (to avoid rework)

Untuk platform NIAGAHUB, anda kena lock 2 decision ini awal:

A) Auth strategy

Supabase Auth untuk staff/admin (recommended)

Customer routes remain public (no login)

B) Merchant identification

slug in URL as primary selector (recommended)

Everything derives merchant_id from slug

Jika anda setuju, langkah seterusnya paling laju ialah:

