SEBELUM KITA START , AKU TAHU SEMUA FUNGSI YANG AKAN ADA ! DAN WUJUD NYA FUNGSI ITU KENAPA ? LIST KAN SEMUA DENGAN DETAILS YANG TERPERINCI

Di bawah ialah full function inventory NIAGAHUB (A‚ÄìZ) untuk ‚Äúsingle app, multi-tenant‚Äù dengan ABANG-COLEK sebagai tenant pertama. Saya pecahkan mengikut domain supaya jelas: fungsi apa wujud, kenapa wujud, siapa guna, dan output/artefak apa. Ini ialah ‚Äúscope lock‚Äù yang boleh terus jadi asas PRD + backlog.

0) Platform Fundamentals
0.1 Multi-Tenancy Core

Fungsi

Merchant scoping via merchant_slug (URL) ‚Üí resolve merchant_id

Theme/branding per merchant (skin)

Data isolation per merchant (RLS + scoped queries)

Multi-location per merchant (kiosk/cawangan)

Kenapa wujud

NIAGAHUB mesti boleh serve ramai peniaga tanpa data bocor.

White-label experience: setiap peniaga rasa ‚Äúapp dia sendiri‚Äù.

User

Semua (customer, staff, admin, platform admin)

Output

Merchant context loaded, UI theme applied, data queries scoped.

1) Public Landing & Merchant Entry
1.1 NIAGAHUB Platform Landing

Fungsi

Value proposition platform

‚ÄúTry Demo‚Äù tenant Abang Colek

Merchant login / onboarding CTA

Product tiers (free/pro) ringkas

Compliance & privacy notice

Kenapa

Conversion funnel: bawa peniaga masuk onboarding, bawa customer masuk order flow.

1.2 Merchant Landing (per tenant)

Fungsi

Merchant profile (nama, lokasi, waktu operasi)

CTA ‚ÄúStart Order‚Äù

CTA ‚ÄúKiosk Mode‚Äù (untuk device kiosk)

Promo/campaign preview (Lucky Draw active)

Kenapa

QR poster biasanya point to merchant landing; user perlukan konteks brand & CTA jelas.

2) Customer Mode (B2C Flow)
2.1 Splash Screen

Fungsi

Brand intro animation, load merchant context

Preload menu + campaign

Kenapa

Brand recall + ‚Äúperceived quality‚Äù; juga warm-up data supaya flow lancar.

2.2 Promo Screen (Campaign Teaser)

Fungsi

Papar Lucky Draw / promo rules (contoh 5:1)

CTA ‚ÄúMulakan Order‚Äù

Auto-skip timer

Kenapa

Naikkan AOV (upsell) sebelum order bermula; set expectation.

2.3 Order Screen (Menu + Voice Assistant optional)

Fungsi

Browse menu, add/remove items

Voice ordering (Nina) + function calling

Real-time cart preview (CRT display untuk tenant yang guna skin CRT)

Upsell prompts (based on rule engine)

Kenapa

Ini engine conversion utama; voice optional tetapi jadi differentiator NIAGAHUB.

2.4 Cart Review

Fungsi

Edit qty, remove item

Show total items, total price

Show eligibility status (Lucky Draw tickets)

CTA upsell ‚ÄúUpgrade to VIP/Combo‚Äù

Kenapa

Kurangkan checkout friction + naikkan AOV.

2.5 Customer Info Capture

Fungsi

Capture WhatsApp number (required jika notifications enabled)

Capture TikTok username (required jika campaign perlukan)

Optional name/email

Consent checkbox (marketing + PDPA-style)

Kenapa

Data capture = moat + remarketing + campaign activation. Tanpa ini, viral loop tak jalan.

2.6 Payment Method Selection

Fungsi

Online payment (Stripe / local provider) optional per merchant

Counter payment (cash/card at counter)

Generate ‚Äúorder code‚Äù jika counter pay

Create order record + payment state

Kenapa

Merchant maturity berbeza: ada yang nak online, ada yang nak manual. NIAGAHUB mesti fleksibel.

2.7 Order Confirmed

Fungsi

Show order number / queue number

Show estimated wait time

Show Lucky Draw ID (jika qualified)

Trigger WhatsApp confirmation (jika enabled)

Subscribe to queue updates

Kenapa

Reduce anxiety; convert ‚Äúwaiting time‚Äù into engagement.

2.8 Selfie Upload (Post-collection activation)

Fungsi

Upload selfie to storage (with product)

Link selfie to lucky_draw_entry

Provide instructions + QR re-entry

Kenapa

Proof-of-participation; juga content factory untuk UGC.

2.9 TikTok Verification (Manual first)

Fungsi

Input TikTok URL / paste link

Basic validation (format)

Set entry status to VERIFIED_PENDING_REVIEW

Optional staff approval toggle later

Kenapa

TikTok API bukan selalu feasible; manual verification ialah ‚Äúgo-live path‚Äù paling cepat.

2.10 Thank You / Completion

Fungsi

Confirm entry status (Activated/Pending)

Remind draw date

CTA reorder / share

Kenapa

Close loop + prompt repeat purchase.

3) Kiosk Mode (On-site Device)
3.1 Kiosk Display Mode

Fungsi

Fullscreen UI, idle attract loop

Direct start order (touch)

Optional voice-first UX (Nina)

Lock kiosk with PIN (staff only)

Kenapa

Untuk booth/kiosk without staff dependency; standardkan ‚Äúself-serve‚Äù experience.

3.2 Kiosk Operational Controls

Fungsi

Quick reset session

