>> # NIAGAHUB
>>
>> NIAGAHUB is a **single-app, multi-tenant commerce operating system** for merchants.
>> It unifies customer ordering, kiosk flows, staff operations, admin control, campaigns, QR-based entry points, and social-driven growth into one platform.
>>
>> ## First Tenant
>> - **ABANG-COLEK** is the first merchant tenant and reference implementation.
>>
>> ## Core Concept
>> NIAGAHUB is not a monolithic ‚Äúfeature app‚Äù. It is an **OS with modular tools**:
>> - merchants can enable/disable capabilities (payments, campaigns, social verification, etc.)
>> - the platform remains lean, scalable, and monetizable
>>
>> ## Routing Model (Multi-Tenant)
>> - Platform: /
>> - Merchant: /m/:slug
>> - Customer: /m/:slug/c/*
>> - Kiosk: /m/:slug/k/*
>> - Staff: /m/:slug/s/*
>> - Admin: /m/:slug/a/*
>>
>> Example (ABANG-COLEK):
>> - /m/abang-colek/c/splash
>>
