1) Codex CLI Prompt ‚Äî PRD.md (Full Production-Ready, A‚ÄìZ)
You are generating a single definitive PRD for the NIAGAHUB platform.

Source-of-truth docs (must comply):
- docs/SYSTEM_LOCK.md
- docs/FINAL_LOCK.md
- docs/VISION.md
- docs/PRODUCT_OVERVIEW.md
