## Tech Stack Summary

| Project | Framework | UI | Database | Purpose |
|---------|-----------|-----|----------|---------|
| **brand-os** | React + Vite | Tailwind CSS | Supabase | Admin Dashboard |
| **kiosk** | React + Vite | Custom CSS | - | POS/Kiosk UI |
| **mobile** | Expo + RN | NativeWind | Drizzle | Mobile App |
| **wocs-server** | Node + Express | - | - | WhatsApp Backend |
| **wocs-extension** | Vanilla JS | CSS | - | Chrome Extension |

